The global Application Release Automation (ARA) market is expected to witness significant growth during the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. The market is segmented based on components, deployments, organization size, and verticals. By component, the market is divided into software and services. The deployment segment includes cloud and on-premises options. Organization size categorizes the market into small and medium-sized enterprises (SMEs) and large enterprises. Furthermore, vertical segmentation covers industries such as BFSI, IT and Telecom, retail, healthcare, manufacturing, and others.

The increasing demand for automation in the software release process across various industries is a key factor driving the growth of the ARA market. Organizations are focusing on streamlining their application release processes to improve efficiency, reduce errors, and enhance overall operational performance. The adoption of cloud-based ARA solutions is also expected to surge, enabling companies to leverage scalability, flexibility, and cost-effectiveness.

